title: Sinag
body:
<<Sinag>>
Help! Help! There’s too many nightmares! I can’t fight them all
...

<<Tala>>
Don’t you worry! I can help you face them!
...

<<Sinag>>
Quick! Fight them before they get us!
...

<<Sinag>>
Wow! Thanks for the help. But now be careful, the next path you are taking in your quest is a bit more dangerous than here...
...

<<Tala>>
I will.
